<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī śakavarṣaṁbulu 1060
<lb n="2"/>gu śāhi Uttarāyaṇa saṁ kāṁti
<lb n="3"/>nimittamusaṁ beddakoṁḍapa nāya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kuṁḍu danataṁ ḍi danaruṁbaṟiti <unclear>nā</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vināyakuniki dharmmārtthamugā sakha
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṁḍavartti dīpaṁbuna kiccina goṟiya
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lu 55 vīniṁ jēkoni kētabōyu<unclear>ni</unclear>
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁḍu danapu trānu pauṭhraka mācaṁ dā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rkamu nityamāneṁḍu neyi voya<unclear>ṁga</unclear>
<lb n="10" break="no"/>la vāṁḍu
</p>

